{"id": "test-02854", "text": "RUGBY UNION - RETIRING CAMPESE WEIGHS UP OPTIONS.", "gold_mentions": [{"start": 0, "end": 11, "ent_type": "ORG", "text": "RUGBY UNION"}, {"start": 23, "end": 30, "ent_type": "PER", "text": "CAMPESE"}]}
{"id": "test-02855", "text": "LONDON 1996-12-07", "gold_mentions": [{"start": 0, "end": 6, "ent_type": "LOC", "text": "LONDON"}]}
{"id": "test-02856", "text": "David Campese will consider offers to play club rugby in England but looks more likely to spend the next year chasing business opportunities in Australia.", "gold_mentions": [{"start": 0, "end": 13, "ent_type": "PER", "text": "David Campese"}, {"start": 57, "end": 64, "ent_type": "LOC", "text": "England"}, {"start": 144, "end": 153, "ent_type": "LOC", "text": "Australia"}]}
{"id": "test-02857", "text": "The 34-year-old winger played his final game in a Wallaby jersey on Saturday but is currently a target for clubs eager to match London side Saracens who have already snapped up Francois Pienaar, Michael Lynagh and Philippe Sella.", "gold_mentions": [{"start": 50, "end": 57, "ent_type": "ORG", "text": "Wallaby"}, {"start": 128, "end": 134, "ent_type": "LOC", "text": "London"}, {"start": 140, "end": 148, "ent_type": "ORG", "text": "Saracens"}, {"start": 177, "end": 193, "ent_type": "PER", "text": "Francois Pienaar"}, {"start": 195, "end": 209, "ent_type": "PER", "text": "Michael Lynagh"}, {"start": 214, "end": 228, "ent_type": "PER", "text": "Philippe Sella"}]}
{"id": "test-02858", "text": "\"If the opportunity is there I'd obviously think about it but the thing that holds me back is business, \"said Campese.", "gold_mentions": [{"start": 110, "end": 117, "ent_type": "PER", "text": "Campese"}]}
{"id": "test-02859", "text": "\"I'd like to come over but there are a lot of things happening at home.", "gold_mentions": []}
{"id": "test-02860", "text": "I've also got a contract to play for New South Wales in the Super 12 next year. \"", "gold_mentions": [{"start": 37, "end": 52, "ent_type": "ORG", "text": "New South Wales"}]}
{"id": "test-02861", "text": "Former Wallaby captain Nick Farr-Jones believes Campese may yet be tempted to England.", "gold_mentions": [{"start": 7, "end": 14, "ent_type": "ORG", "text": "Wallaby"}, {"start": 23, "end": 38, "ent_type": "PER", "text": "Nick Farr-Jones"}, {"start": 48, "end": 55, "ent_type": "PER", "text": "Campese"}, {"start": 78, "end": 85, "ent_type": "LOC", "text": "England"}]}
{"id": "test-02862", "text": "\"I'm sure there are a few people in England who'd be delighted to have David Campese in their club's jersey, \"he said.", "gold_mentions": [{"start": 36, "end": 43, "ent_type": "LOC", "text": "England"}, {"start": 71, "end": 84, "ent_type": "PER", "text": "David Campese"}]}
{"id": "test-02863", "text": "SOCCER - ENGLISH PREMIER LEAGUE SUMMARIES.", "gold_mentions": [{"start": 9, "end": 16, "ent_type": "MISC", "text": "ENGLISH"}]}
